</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
44 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
REGIONAL ROUNDUP: ALPHAREL RECEIVES $800,000 SUBCONTRACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Alpharel Inc., a struggling Camarillo maker of data storage devices, has 
received an $800,000 subcontract to provide an image-management system that 
will be used for publishing applications. Alpharel would not identify the 
primary contractors or the customer. 
</P>
