</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NOTICE TO READERS: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Business deadlines for today were earlier than usual to allow the fullest 
possible coverage of the Academy Awards. Financial tables that arrived past 
those earlier deadlines -- including Mutual Funds, Options and Treasury issues 
-- appear on A30 and A31. 
</P>
