<P>
ESPIONAGE -- EAST GERMANY; EAST GERMANY -- GOVERNMENT; EAST GERMANY -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; GOVERNMENT REFORM; POLICE -- EAST GERMANY; INTELLIGENCE 
