<P>
A comparison of median home prices by region for the months of February, 1989, 
and February, 1990. 
</P>
<TABLE CWL="3.87IN:2.66IN:2.66IN" WDM="ABS" NCOLS="3">
<ROWRULE>  </ROWRULE>
<TABLEROW>
<CELLRULE>  </CELLRULE>
<TABLECELL CHJ="C" CVJ="C">
